Package: quantoscript
Version: 0.1.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libssl3 | libssl1.1
Maintainer: QuantoScript Project <quanto@quantoscript.dev>
Description: Dynamically-typed language with try/oops and bytecode VM
 QuantoScript is a dynamically-typed interpreted language with
 try/oops exception handling and an AST-based bytecode virtual
 machine. It supports functions, closures, collections, and a
 standard library for HTTP, WebSocket, and file I/O.
